snippet.title: Call Me Swal
snippet.description:
The best way to learn engineering is by trying (and sometimes failing) to make stuff, not trying to pass a test. That’s why I attempt to build increasingly ambitious things. I document my projects as best I can on this channel so other people can follow along. If a few people start building stuff because of my videos, I’ll be stoked!




Goal: 10,000 subscribers by December 2021. Writing it here so I have to meet it :)
Official PCB Sponsor: https://jlcpcb.com/. Use coupon code "JLCPCBcom"
Old Channel Names: Call Me Swal, Swaleh Owais, 3 Idiots Engineering Youtube Channel
